snippet.title: Swift: FB Messenger - How to create a Tab Bar Menu, Cell Highlights, NSDate formats (Ep 4)
snippet.description:
Today we learn how to programmatically create a custom UITabBarController and set it as our main root view controller on AppDelegate.  Next we'll go through how to create a highlight when selected a cell. Finally we take a look a some additional date formats for NSDate.

(Part 1) Building out the UI with Auto Layout in Code / Programmatically: https://youtu.be/XtEoKixIfG4
(Part 2) Core Data - Create, Read, and Delete Entities:
https://youtu.be/TW_jcvVvPwI
(Part 3) Core Data - NSSortDescriptor, NSPredicate: https://youtu.be/hz1h_ColGy0

Completed Source Code:
https://www.letsbuildthatapp.com/course/Facebook-Chat-Messenger
